<br>
Getting rid of twinking is kinda a double edged sword. Makes lower levels harder... (yay?) but (? again) makes the reward for getting up there less. Makes new guys feel less cheated, but... I don't think I've ever been very pissed by twinks, except when they're asses and do things they shouldn't anyways.<br>
